{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "finance-training-api-v3",
    "name": "Finance Training API v3",
    "description": "Loan management system — Customer, Loan Application, Repayment Schedule (auto-generated), Payment Transaction.\n\nKey changes v3:\n- Schedule auto-generated when loan status becomes DISBURSED (no manual endpoint)\n- Payment auto-updates schedule to PAID when total paid >= total_amount\n- Specific error codes (CUSTOMER_NOT_FOUND, LOAN_APPLICATION_NOT_FOUND, etc.)\n\nPrerequisites:\n- docker compose up -d (PostgreSQL)\n- ./mvnw spring-boot:run (app on :8080)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
